OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1772021941
OL,3,CFor the first time this year Jersey is
OL,4,Cexpecting two consecutive dry days
OL,6,FThe Jersey Met office is expecting the
OL,7,Fisland to have the first two
OL,8,Fconsecutive dry days of the year on
OL,9,FFebruary 24 and 25.
OL,11,FIt comes after January and February
OL,12,Frainfall has been twice what we would
OL,13,Fnormally expect, with one two-day
OL,14,Fperiod (17 and 18 February) seeing
OL,15,Fmore than 60 mm of rain in Jersey and
OL,16,F40 mm in Guernsey.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/3
