OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1772021941
OL,3,CFor the first time this year Jersey is
OL,4,Cexpecting two consecutive dry days
OL,6,FBut be warned, the Channel Islands
OL,7,Fhave experienced significant snowfall
OL,8,Fat the beginning of March -
OL,9,Fforecasters are saying the region is
OL,10,Fnot quite out of the woods yet.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/3
